Class TagFile

java.lang.Object
io.github.weblegacy.tlddoc.tagfileparser.javacc.TagFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
TagFileConstants, TagFileTreeConstants
public class TagFile extends Object implements TagFileTreeConstants, TagFileConstants
Simple parser for tag files that only actually parses the directives. All other content is left unparsed.
Author:
Mark Roth
